    • BreakerFiducialPhotonTarget

      public BreakerFiducialPhotonTarget​(int fiducialID, edu.wpi.first.math.geometry.Pose3d targetPose, BreakerPhotonCamera... cameras)
      AprilTag/fiducial marker for cameras to track.
      Parameters:
      fiducialID - - The numeric ID of the Fidicial Marker, this is tied to the tag's pattern and is constant.
      targetPose - - The 3 dimensional orientation of the target relative the the field origin.
      cameras - - Any and all cameras that will be used to track the target.
